21 September 2016 - Nicksoul and friends have done it again, this time they remix Babes womdumo's Wololo JOHANNESBURG - Bongekile Simelane is a 23-year-old dancer, singer and entertainer, popularly known by her stage name Babes Wodumo. Her hit song Wololo has been playing all over local radio recently. In the video below Nicholas Nkuna Nicksoul and friends do a Scatamiya rendition of the popular house song.  Nicksoul is no stranger to the lime-light. From a rural home in Mpumalanga to lights, cameraÂ and action in the acting industry, we know him for his role in Skeem Saam. He has been making waves on social media with his African remixes of popular songs.